The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: fantasy, superhero
The people have 2 different jobs:  writer, project-manager
1. the writer is on the right of the person watching superhero movies##1
2. the person eating pomegranate is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |
| Food          | pomegranate | raspberry |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero   | fantasy   |
| Job     | project-manager       | writer      |

